<section class="ingredients-section" id="ingredients">
  <div class="ingredients-header reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">From the depths of nature to the depths of you.</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Ingredients that<br><em>transform</em></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="ingredients-grid">
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Surfalux</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">A cutting-edge technology combining gentle yet efficient surfactants for thorough cleansing without dryness. The backbone of Foundation Shampoo.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Niacinamide &amp; Urea</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">Moisturizing actives that penetrate the skin, regenerating cells and maintaining a healthy scalp microbiome. In Foundation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Xylitol</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">Repairs scalp and hair cuticles, enhancing shine, curl definition, and volume control. In Foundation &amp; Wavemaker.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Açaí &amp; Pequi Oils</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">Antioxidant-rich Açaí restores vitality. Pequi, rich in vitamins A and E, softens, hydrates and strengthens. Trinity.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Murumuru &amp; Cupuaçu</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">Murumuru seals moisture and reduces frizz. Cupuaçu delivers intense hydration and elasticity. Trinity.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Vegan Protein Trio</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">Hydrolyzed Corn, Wheat &amp; Soy Proteins reinforce the hair fiber, improving resilience and reducing breakage. Titan.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Hyaluronic Acid</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">A moisture magnet that hydrates and plumps the hair, supporting bounce and a fuller feel. Titan Booster.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Marshmallow, Linseed &amp; Chia</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">Wavemaker&rsquo;s botanical trio. Creates a flexible film that defines waves and curls without stiffness.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Jojoba, Pracaxi &amp; Abyssinian</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">Jojoba mimics natural lipids; Pracaxi and Abyssinian deliver a sleek, satin finish with shine and frizz control. Nectar.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Kukui &amp; Avocado Oils</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">Sink in with richness, supporting elasticity and suppleness. Tocopherol (Vitamin E) seals and protects. Nectar.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Radish Root Ferment</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">Microbiome-friendly prebiotic and ferment that keeps Titan gentle and scalp-comforting.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card reveal"><div class="ingredient-icon">&#9670;</div>
      <h3 class="ingredient-name">Lavender &amp; Rosemary Waters</h3>
      <p class="ingredient-desc">Aromatic hydrosols in Titan that soothe the scalp while providing a fresh, comfortable cleanse.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% schema %}{"name":"Ingredients","settings":[]}{% endschema %}
